description: Gold Mountain Mining Corp. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Canada. It explores for gold and silver deposits. The company owns 100% interest in the Elk Gold project that consists of 32 mineral claims covering 22,152 hectares and two mining lease covering 646 hectares located in the South Central, British Columbia. The company was formerly known as Freeform Capital Partners Inc. and changed its name to Gold Mountain Mining Corp. in December 2020. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Ronald V. Woo B.Sc., M.B.A., P.Eng., P.M.P.
